#include <bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;
vector<bool> prime(10000,true);
vector<int> v;
void compute()
{
	for(int p=2;p<=10000;p++)
	{
		if(prime[p]==true)
		{
			for(int i=2*p;i<=10000;i=i+p)
			{
				prime[i]=false;
			}
			v.push_back(p); 
		}
	}
}

int main()
{
	compute();
	int n,k;
	cin>>n>>k;
	int cnt=0;
	bool flag=false;
	int i=0;
	while(v[i]+v[i+1]+1<=n)
	{
		int k=v[i]+v[i+1];
		if(binary_search(v.begin(),v.end(),k+1)){
			cnt++;
		}
		i++;
	} 

	if(cnt>=k)cout<<"YES\n";
	else cout<<"NO\n";
}
